    <item>
      <title>醫美新規怎麼看？消費者自保四步驟</title>
      <link>https://deepgill1004-hue.github.io/feifei-yubai-site/letters/010-aesthetic-regulation-checklist.html</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://deepgill1004-hue.github.io/feifei-yubai-site/letters/010-aesthetic-regulation-checklist.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 May 2026 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
      <description><![CDATA[不要只看裝潢與優惠，先查人、查場地、查產品、查救護流程。]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[
        <p>所有漂亮話都要落回四件事：誰做、在哪裡做、用什麼做、出事誰救。</p>
        <p><a href="https://deepgill1004-hue.github.io/feifei-yubai-site/letters/010-aesthetic-regulation-checklist.html">閱讀完整文章</a></p>
