    <item>
      <title>醫美「舒眠麻醉」前，先確認三件事</title>
      <link>https://deepgill1004-hue.github.io/feifei-yubai-site/letters/005-aesthetic-anesthesia-risk.html</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://deepgill1004-hue.github.io/feifei-yubai-site/letters/005-aesthetic-anesthesia-risk.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 May 2026 13:35:00 GMT</pubDate>
      <description><![CDATA[牛奶針不是保養，任何需要鎮靜或麻醉的療程都要先問誰執行、用什麼、怎麼救。]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[
        <p>聽起來像睡一下，實際上仍是麻醉與鎮靜。風險不在名字，在現場有沒有能力處理意外。</p>
        <p><a href="https://deepgill1004-hue.github.io/feifei-yubai-site/letters/005-aesthetic-anesthesia-risk.html">閱讀完整文章</a></p>
      ]]></content:encoded>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>線雕拉提前，先問三個問題</title>
